# Pull Request Checklist

- [ ] I identified all affected ADRs.
- [ ] I identified all affected invariants.
- [ ] I listed the acceptance tests before coding.
- [ ] I did not change architecture without an ADR update.
- [ ] I did not touch unrelated modules.
- [ ] I verified recovery behavior if config, logging, menu, or startup code changed.
- [ ] I verified import invariants if calendar, state, duplicate, table, or sync logic changed.
